    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "Reference is made to a memorandum to Mr. Harbo from Mr. Baughman",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "on the above-captioned matter, dated September 3, 1947. The reference",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "memorandum indicates that the instrument has been examined by the Laboratory",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "and the laboratory had contacted a Mrs. Whedon of the Army Engineers and she",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "indicated that the instrument had been used by the Air Forces on tests which",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "were classified as \"Top Secret.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "The memorandum indicates that Special Agent S. W. Reynolds of the Liaison",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "Section contacted the Intelligence Division of the Air Forces and was advised that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "Mrs. Whedon alluded that the instrument was used in \"Operation Mogul.\" The instru-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "ment was loaned to the Intelligence Division of the Air Forces who in turn forwarded",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "it to Wright Field. The report was received from Wright Field indicating the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "instrument had no connection with \"Operation Mogul\" or any other operation at Wright",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "Field. It was classified as a hoax in view of the apparent discrepancy between",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "information developed from Mrs. Whedon and information received from Intelligence",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "Division of the Air Forces that the Bureau might wish to pursue this matter further.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "Mr. Zimmers of the Technical Laboratory advised Mr. Reynolds of the Liaison",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "Section that Mrs. Whedon had told him that a Major Hopkins handled the Liaison in",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "Washington for the tests in which this instrument was used. Lieutenant Colonel George",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "Garrett of the Intelligence Division of the Air Forces advised Special Agent Reynolds",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "that he contacted Major Hopkins. He advised that Major Hopkins has had a great deal",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "of experience in radio and along technical lines. Major Hopkins advised Colonel",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "Garrett that the instrument could not have been used in the \"Operation Mogul.\" Hopkins",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "text": "indicated that from the pictures and particles recovered, it appeared to him to be a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "text": "part or portions of an old-type radio loud speaker.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "text": "In view of the information received from Major Hopkins, Colonel Garrett",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "text": "stated that he was at a loss as to how to explain the actions of Mrs. Whedon other",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "text": "than to say that she perhaps gave a false impression as to her knowledge of the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "text": "instrument and the \"Operation Mogul.\" Garrett pointed out that in view of the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "report received from Wright Field, together with the statement made by Major Hopkins,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "he felt that there was sufficient evidence that this instrument was not used in any",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "text": "War Department classified project and that in all probability it was just a hoax.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "text": "Air Force",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 67,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68,
      "text": "RECOMMENDATION: It is recommended that this memorandum be forwarded to",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 69,
      "text": "the Technical Laboratory for their information.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
